  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>패키지, 박스 소량 생산은</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ee34c440-e61b-4045-a48d-1ba96698a31e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-ee34c440-e61b-4045-a48d-1ba96698a31e\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MTlfMjAg/MDAxNzUyODk4MTA3NDQ4.T4-SsoEPlk2Z0NOnHrH_cSjsG5Rg-W4A6qwucaWEzb4g.vCIOD2o5BTUjWDIgS7TlcUQ6Qxzmuumyty63G2bnwUwg.PNG/Box_Mockup_4.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"4000\", \"originalHeight\" : \"3000\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MTlfMjAg/MDAxNzUyODk4MTA3NDQ4.T4-SsoEPlk2Z0NOnHrH_cSjsG5Rg-W4A6qwucaWEzb4g.vCIOD2o5BTUjWDIgS7TlcUQ6Qxzmuumyty63G2bnwUwg.PNG/Box_Mockup_4.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-7350edcb-30cb-4bbd-ab87-5a1f99926fb7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e8abbcd6-6939-49d5-9eb7-725d2a5e290c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-91b45a36-9c5d-4d71-af05-ceaf22deb1c6\" style=\"\">단상자의 수량 기준</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">단상자의 최소 수량 문의가 급증하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-34ccd4b7-ad53-4614-8c11-5ed9467a8bbd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c2cc55d9-5339-4031-a6b3-5d7e1c119397\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fa957017-2fcb-404c-b394-6ef8179b4b54\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5cad45ce-f3ab-4251-a313-eaa6c231099b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 주문 수량은 제한이 없습니다. 1개도 제작이 가능한 시대가 왔습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8656c76b-be0d-4fa3-9c91-3d279cc20f0a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-83815b35-8646-4ab5-8bc9-c739d33b3a12\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-49f87167-02a9-4b10-b6f8-ab64d85d6c54\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5b0fb574-46a2-4103-879f-3191022d9978\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 샘플용이나 촬영 소품용을 제외하고는 포장 패키지는 판매원가에 포함이 되는 요소이므로 주문 수량별로 단가가 무척 중요합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c3ea5c6e-8ad2-4a4f-9917-2841a65aac7f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-bc33def9-9761-4bb8-b2cf-5ec9481e6cfb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e71b4acf-a206-495b-8034-8b1df9becf9e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-716dca70-a194-4c74-94e1-5d4d689d7a84\" style=\"color:#555555;\">사이즈에 따라 물론 원가가 달라지지만 통상적으로는 1,000개 이상 주문을 해야 어느 정도 단가를 맞출 수 있습니다. 이 부분도 더 많이 주문할수록 원가가 줄어드는 것은 너무도 당연합니다. 1,000개보다는 10,000개가 @당 단가는 훨씬 더 저렴해질 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d2f1d50a-89d6-4eeb-ab3e-eb576d75bb64\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-53c8055b-e9a3-41aa-863f-1ac357e3e8b7\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7b91c8c6-d096-4799-8109-1253facd675a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-621385b6-425e-4c79-8941-64aed4465aa3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">판매가 확실하고 원가가 중요하시다면 대량으로 발주하여 원가를 줄이시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5fa862e2-859f-458d-be2d-9c10ee23c7e9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-26f2a597-e32c-4e12-9a8d-b845a1a8a6ed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ed28863c-d157-4744-be8d-db7dbba5bd59\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-22141e47-1093-4367-8b58-418c75545dd1\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>소량 발주 : 1개부터</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a132b5a7-efc4-40ea-b290-6deb4e1725fc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-48874bc5-18b5-46d0-b35f-c2bc672dd003\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>대량 발주 : 1,000개 이상</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c1fd65b3-3bf1-4097-a8f5-846ac1af1d34\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5d9739ea-53e8-41a3-8304-20f35612bdc3\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5a7deb61-5a19-4966-aa04-3802c0671d5a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-0011742e-8002-4324-9a4e-62ec8f4a81fa\" style=\"color:#54b800;\"><b>단상자에 맞는 후공정</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-36ab2e02-cbb8-4f66-bff4-40c7dd4a78f4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cad4ad21-b167-43bd-88d0-53494d496a53\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b4b9d910-8983-485c-ae58-99e91cee056c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-14d7667a-b746-49ac-ad77-e5e5f6493b06\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>별색인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b08e2250-6f2a-41cb-9352-71b5f6b3dd1e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-79d5c35e-79a3-4de9-906a-572567056798\" style=\"color:#555555;\">별색인쇄는 그 제품의 브랜드를 살릴 수 있는 가장 좋은 방법입니다. 재 발주 시 중요 로고나 브랜드의 색상이 달라질 일이 적고 더 돋보이게 색상을 구현함으로써 보다 퀄리티 있는 브랜드를 만들 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-ca1b5e7f-b4f1-44ad-bcb4-ea3829b4c3f5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9c2fa924-a423-4c60-8578-cb29dd488f65\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-30de4ff0-b9e6-4db7-a977-36889c34d590\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-fa3a1857-61d9-4688-97c4-8789e312e40f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-fa3a1857-61d9-4688-97c4-8789e312e40f\", \"link\": \"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223722537449\"}' data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223722537449\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/223722537449</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-49ab6967-4a26-4854-8b46-19ce5c67736f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d3141e93-cb58-4214-ae06-ff9a21bc4715\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-02cbebef-fb8b-4f26-a915-a1b827bb53f0\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-02cbebef-fb8b-4f26-a915-a1b827bb53f0\", \"link\": \"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223863168806\"}' data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223863168806\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/223863168806</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0da85748-57d2-4590-8185-be2b2a7ed1b4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-87637a88-1711-41da-ae8d-4c6aa3df8326\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c8b693c6-4ebe-49a2-81ff-ed453b0cb567\" style=\"color:#555555;\">별색은 몇 가지 고려 사항이 있습니다. 그중 하나는 단가입니다. 평량이 높은 종이에 별색인쇄를 하려면 통상의 경우는 UV 인쇄기로 작업을 하게 됩니다. 이럴 경우 일반 인쇄 비용보다 많게는 3~5배의 단가가 증가할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e778491c-0348-42f7-a521-2c72d3587b88\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5813a112-eec6-492d-a8b8-185fb9f0b17d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e328d752-230e-4a9d-9f49-f1488fed0899\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-71415c19-3879-4f40-aa4e-5cbbdcf6c17c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 이런 단가의 중가를 고려하더라도 별색으로 자사의 브랜드를 높여 작업하는 것은 중요합니다. 특히 일반적인 단상자가 아닌 퀄리티 높은 제품의 단상자인 경우는 반드시 별색으로 처리하여 패키지의 퀄리티를 높일 것을 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2fe7e3cd-b784-427f-9826-c02f217f5759\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2195e8d3-a907-45e3-b9f6-25ec42856624\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5c6e77ed-d128-4fbb-a9a1-e02e412ccbc9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9c97ae62-2a3a-404c-8820-908f6e6724c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">또 하나 주의할 것은 작업 방법입니다. 별색인쇄를 사용하여 인쇄물을 주문해 보지 않은 대부분의 디자이너 분이 4도와의 혼용 작업으로 디자인할 경우 실수를 하는 사례를 여러 차례 경험하였습니다. 이런 사고를 방지하기 위해 반드시 (주)파파스컴퍼니과 상의하여 작업해 주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ca526fce-dfb8-46a3-b61e-bf2d960fb506\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n<a class=\"se-module se-module-talktalk\" href=\"https://talk.naver.com/w4tbeb?frm=mblog&amp;ref=https%3A%2F%2Fm.blog.naver.com%2Fcookthedesign%2F223939442327#nafullscreen\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.talktalk', '');\">\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c0a2de92-be83-4dd4-9933-5b372c7ad910\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6009885c-d75f-46eb-bde4-d9340f9aa18a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-7dedcccf-3e82-4638-a083-730e491708df\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-266ada4a-bc95-4104-98b6-e3b83a7baf70\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-037e66a5-00ad-447f-98fc-49244e642bde\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>박인쇄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d146e2e6-4068-4c98-8334-9da49836edf9\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-d909574b-0c54-45fa-8d9b-4ea683e34d48\" style=\"color:#555555;\">박인쇄는 가장 일반적인 후공정 기법입니다. 금박이나 은박으로 멋을 낼 수 있고 또는 홀로그램이나 특별한 박지를 사용할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ce03901-3a13-40c9-845a-35ecc69abe04\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5af357ec-aebe-4878-9532-a3f1fc700235\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-5af357ec-aebe-4878-9532-a3f1fc700235\", \"link\": \"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223892177638\"}' data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223892177638\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/223892177638</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-eea5d3cd-2adf-4e45-af8d-81444a0292e5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-13576e77-2eab-4f91-aae0-dacecd765333\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-df3461a2-5aca-4d23-a673-d2ef0a845757\" style=\"color:#555555;\">박인쇄의 종류도 무척이나 다양하고 요즘은 로즈 골드 박이나 핑크 박등 특별한 박형식도 많이 사용하기 때문에 샘플을 보고 판단하시는 것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-cc1a494f-738b-4c02-908c-f2676666f469\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-f81b4307-e5a0-4720-a87b-cd5813e16905\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-40d7ef57-ce61-4209-b6af-44741d58569e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4cfe18cd-e097-4f57-8acb-ca727a8b46a4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">방문 상담이나 기타 방법으로 상담은 가능합니다. 하지만 저희도 순차적으로 진행하고 있거나 여러 가지를 고려하여 방문상담 신청을 받고 있으니 참고하여 주시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1bea0a49-2bff-40d7-8c33-9544f34689af\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a7651b72-57d3-4295-96ff-7562617ea3d0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-041f14cd-8a0b-46ed-8b67-558371935c7f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c3dfea7f-fd29-4e5b-8c04-8e67ff057fa1\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>형압</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9e4c2f49-d0ee-482c-8cfd-d46fc0995b9f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-19737f12-0ebf-4d47-9be1-fd3cdec516c8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오목과 볼록으로 종이를 눌러 표현하는 기법입니다. 박인쇄를 하고 더 돋보이게 하기 위해 형압으로 마무리할 수도 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-db1984ad-6152-41bd-b6a0-cf1d1ad20321\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2816214a-aa30-4f7a-9f17-746bfa65caed\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-74f1fab8-6b0d-419b-8a53-7cb9cbfedd0c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-de3f3d59-31d6-4fdd-a7c9-0630b2e0f90b\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><a class=\"se-link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\": \"SE-de3f3d59-31d6-4fdd-a7c9-0630b2e0f90b\", \"link\": \"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223803578383\"}' data-linktype=\"text\" href=\"https://blog.naver.com/cookthedesign/223803578383\" target=\"_blank\">https://blog.naver.com/(주)파파스컴퍼니/223803578383</a></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> \n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9d151132-0249-4ded-89e2-9a90fb8203ae\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5735e259-03b7-4833-8b01-5a85ac4a3f3a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-9851967c-f9d8-400f-87c9-d2c46c03a252\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-3b31f400-58a7-4f19-9bf7-703c0af8e457\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-782b6396-6da9-4427-b2aa-cfde75fd6eba\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>에폭시, 부분 코팅 등</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-72d1cb0f-e14e-45e7-b1ab-11b71ac73eab\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-19ff731d-e446-4f3e-899e-29da086d052f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">후공정은 다양하고 용어도 완벽하게 정의되고 있지는 않습니다. 가장 중요한 것은 고객님께서 하고 싶은 후공정의 사진을 보내주시는 것이 가장 좋습니다. 글보다는 이미지로 이미지와 함께 동영상까지 주시면 견적을 내는 데 도움이 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1763b4f0-1876-47ac-966b-c2e0acb25a2c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5c7709e0-74d0-470e-a46f-65f4938851a6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b873a843-0f37-4ebb-9c3a-a672022653ed\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-2ce728ee-17c3-4fe7-8037-3806122cb22f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">견적요청은 (주)파파스컴퍼니 사이트 견적문의 창을 이용해 주시면 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-92b7c540-d63b-47b8-bdfe-2d4bf33a46fd\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-92b7c540-d63b-47b8-bdfe-2d4bf33a46fd\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MTlfMjI3/MDAxNzUyODk5NzkwODgz.5jmhIDPawBoBEFR8dsUL1Tsng1ErpmvGo_hKmWueqpwg.Tcypyt-zYcKGTKntbWscdWPhFXQLpUm6jOAZ7XdqBCkg.PNG/SE-364dcdda-6c07-42aa-a5f7-3f3628914ba6.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1797\", \"originalHeight\" : \"971\", \"linkUse\" : \"true\", \"link\" : \"https://cookthedesign.co.kr\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTA3MTlfMjI3/MDAxNzUyODk5NzkwODgz.5jmhIDPawBoBEFR8dsUL1Tsng1ErpmvGo_hKmWueqpwg.Tcypyt-zYcKGTKntbWscdWPhFXQLpUm6jOAZ7XdqBCkg.PNG/SE-364dcdda-6c07-42aa-a5f7-3f3628914ba6.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-690f2268-12b9-4146-846a-81c111787e62\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-beb33d7b-2966-4c59-8ecb-9b2cd81a50be\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-22e3ebbb-3012-48d5-a683-f5d7faefa4da\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-a1d5b864-1212-4848-a122-c4fa35e0abcf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b9307a18-21a8-4b27-b0b6-aef240e0984b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">홈페이지 문의도 좋지만 직접 통화만큼 좋은 것은 없습니다. (주)파파스컴퍼니은 더 정확한 견적을 보내드리기 위해 항상 통화를 진행하고 있습니다. 가끔 회사나 정보를 노출하기 싫어하시는 고객님도 계십니다. 그런 분은 네이버 톡톡이나 사이트 문의를 남겨주세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7bd6f169-550c-46d8-a51a-c09e37c1559b\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-7bd6f169-550c-46d8-a51a-c09e37c1559b\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-p